1859年大西洋飓风季首场风暴的相关记录很少，是在1995年[[气象学|气象学家]]何塞·费尔南德斯-帕塔加斯（{{lang|en|Jose Fernandez-Partagás}}）和亨利·迪亚兹（{{lang|en|Henry Diaz}}）出版的文献中首度记载<ref name="Partagas1">{{cite web | last1 = Partagás | first1 = José Fernández | last2 = Diaz | first2 = Henry | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2003 | title = A Reconstruction of Historical Tropical Cyclone Frequency in the Atlantic from Documentary and other Historical Sources: Year 1859 | accessdate = 2016-11-26 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054357/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1858-1864/1859.pdf | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/Landsea/Partagas/1858-1864/1859.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>{{rp|1}}。6月底或7月初，墨西哥[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]多个沿海城市受到强烈飓风袭击，[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]有许多船只失踪。由于缺乏观测纪录，大西洋飓风数据库中只确认气旋曾于7月1日在韦拉克鲁斯州图斯潘（{{lang|en|Tuxpan}}）附近经过，而且对这个日期也没有足够把握。<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = National Hurricane Center | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] }}</ref><ref name="meta">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Division | year = 2011 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161124024737/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_master.html | deadurl = no | title = Documentation of Atlantic Tropical Cyclones Changes in HURDAT | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-11-26 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/metadata_master.html | archivedate = 2016-11-24 }}</ref>估计风暴的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]达到每小时165公里，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="HURDAT" />。
